Multi-threading compressors test.
They include pbzip2, pigz, plzip, pixz, zstd, zstd-mt.


Run ./1-prep.sh to prepare programs (download and compile).
Then ./2-test.sh to do the test.

In windoze run MSYS terminal with msys_rxvt.bat, msys_mintty.bat or msys_cmd.bat,
whichever runs first. Then in terminal go to the test directory, i.e.:
~~~
C:\temp\mt-comp-test_msys \> msys_rxvt.bat

$ cd "C:\temp\mt-comp-test_msys"
$ ./1-prep.sh
$ ./2-test.sh
~~~

in *nix use /tmp.

